  <brief_title>Treatment of Philadelphia-Positive Acute Lymphocytic Leukemia (Ph+ ALL) in the Elderly With Imatinib Mesylate (STI571) and Chemotherapy.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Imatinib (GLIVEC) After Induction Therapy in Patients Aged More Than 55 Years With Philadelphia Positive Acute Lymphoblastic Leukaemia (Ph+ ALL) : a Non Randomised, Controlled, Open, Multicentric, International Phase II Clinical Study (CSTI 571 AFR09 Trial)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
